des: The Cooking with Cheetos experience with Alexa gives you a chance to turn boring food into better-tasting food with delicious Cheetos recipe suggestions from Chef Chester Cheetah. This skill uses Alexa Shopping to make purchases on Amazon. Alexa allows purchasing by voice using your default payment and shipping settings. You can set a voice confirmation code, turn off purchasing, and see product and order details in your Alexa app.
